data.description:
This two-story single family home with SOLAR built in 2002 located in the European Quarter gated community has approximately 1828 sqft, an open floor plan, living room, dining area, hardwood floors, carpet flooring throughout, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, electric range, dishwasher, garbage disposal, built in microwave, refrigerator, laundry room with washer & dryer, central heat & air, ceiling fans, gas fireplace, 2-car garage with electric opener, Front and backyard with automatic sprinklers; Yard Service Included
 From N. Willow Ave and E. Teague ave, turn onto N. Monaco Lane, then left onto W. Barcelona Lane. Close to schools, parks, shopping. Addenda to be signed: CC&R's; BBQ not for tenant use. Renter's Insurance Required. One Year Lease Required. Pets very strictly negotiable (1 small pet under 20lbs).
